{"tid":1835696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣交通部擬取消春節期間10個陸客團","createTime":"2020-01-23T02:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:52:22.000Z","uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f87af2a1c2592551204c6d858b99c5c625eaf75","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"因應武漢肺炎，交通部上午召開內部應變會議，針對23號小年夜將有兩團來自武漢陸客團抵台，春節期間到1月29日，還會8團陸續抵達。交通部表將透過相關窗口與對岸溝通，希望對岸可以取消這10團，178人來台的行程。<br />\n<br />\n針對台灣團前往武漢部分，春節期間原本七團，但因應旅遊警示升級為第三級，目前都已經取消。旅行業者會依照觀光局要求，協助民眾退費或轉團。品保協會發言人李奇嶽說：「按照觀光局的指示來辦理，想要協助轉團的就協助轉團，要求要退費的就退費。」<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業者表示，其實武漢並非中國旅遊熱點，往返當地其實以台商居多，擔心疫情擴散。上午不少從中國返台的台商，都自主配戴口罩。上海台商表示，「大陸人也會懷疑說，是不是人數一定不只是這樣，對。（所以你現在身體狀況都還好？）對，就趕快逃回來。」香港返台民眾也說：「香港人因為經過SARS，所以他們對這種東西都特別謹慎，所以平常地鐵什麼的，戴口罩的人都多了。」"},{"pid":"65ab906d63afc20c0b159fecfaf67e54cf431d37","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:39:28.000Z","msg":"邊境防疫人員也戴起口罩，專注盯著紅外線螢幕，篩檢出發燒旅客。兩大航空公司也針對飛航中港澳航線的第一線服勤機組員，提供口罩。華航則宣布，啟動自主防疫措施，飛航武漢班機回收的毛毯，將加強曝曬與消毒，避免成為感染媒介。<br />\n<img src=\"http://news.pts.org.tw/news_images/463869/1579677501b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Fnews_images%2F463869%2F1579677501b.jpg&h=5d6d5f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://news.pts.org.tw/news_images/463869/1579677502d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Fnews_images%2F463869%2F1579677502d.jpg&h=a28f6a25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d117afce3b32789b38853a07b6e1462973b8a764","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/463869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F463869&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzPBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=50f4d23d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/463869</a>"},{"pid":"b0903ade344ce2e8ed7a47303792cdc44529b3ea","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"目前在台8團、130名武漢旅客，觀光局均有掌握動態，已要求領隊、導遊每日掌握旅客體溫及身體狀況有無異常，定期通報，並要求團員於密閉空間要配戴口罩。<br />\n　<br />\n#武漢肺炎 #觀光局 #旅行團<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3048276?fbclid=IwAR1ccQbu93dfDVwaNv0P3UWMfOu6wu_nrkfOeTde0FCdsPO7ODyNLdcx1rk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048276%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ccQbu93dfDVwaNv0P3UWMfOu6wu_nrkfOeTde0FCdsPO7ODyNLdcx1rk&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzPBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=f8ded21b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3048276%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ccQbu93dfDVwaNv0P3UWMfOu6wu_nrkfOeTde0FCdsPO7ODyNLdcx1rk&h=b7dc0af4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3048276?fbclid=IwAR1ccQbu93dfDVwaNv0P3UWMfOu6wu_nrkfOeTde0FCdsPO7ODyNLdcx1rk</a>"},{"pid":"df250eb6ebb74a9dd8f42ea24b55fe7b42c5364b","tid":1835696,"uid":81628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:42:19.000Z","msg":"台灣都識取消<br />\n香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb7cbdb171c98347f36cd364ed796907b8673a","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"其實直接取消咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaac4f8e633048cc5a92ab6cbd40d7fe2012e1b8","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，台灣昨日確診首宗病例。在台灣，總統蔡英文今日發表談話，指已請求交通部要求台灣旅遊業者，確定所有武漢旅遊團暫停出團，並暫停武漢旅遊團來台。"},{"pid":"660b8e3a2676d275b738a7077fca1ca305c36fca","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaac4f8e633048cc5a92ab6cbd40d7fe2012e1b8","tid":1835696,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:50:45.00